      "content": "exactly. it's like people think there's always a way back to \"normal,\" but what if there isn't? what if some damage is just... final? what if i'm just a broken machine that was meant to be scrapped a long time ago? it feels so much more logical to just stop fighting a losing battle than to keep pretending there's a cure.",
